<p>

<b>Sampurnanand Sanskrit University</b> is an institution of higher learning in oriental learning, <language wordnetid="106282651" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../698/27698.xml">
Sanskrit</link></language>
 allied areas, etc. and is located in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../177/236177.xml">
Benares</link> which is also known as <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.8">
<region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<administrative_district wordnetid="108491826" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
